Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MC大奖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:10.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其一  提案
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.51,0:00:12.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次的学园祭演唱会要…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.64,0:00:13.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演唱会要？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.90,0:00:17.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠MC活跃气氛！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.42,0:00:19.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.94,0:00:21.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是应该靠演奏来活跃气氛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.37,0:00:23.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演奏自然也很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.63,0:00:26.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但根据我在暗中进行的问卷调查中显示
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.90,0:00:28.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家最希望在轻音部看到的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.39,0:00:30.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑话！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.47,0:00:33.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都给谁做的问卷调查啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.93,0:00:38.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就让最搞笑的部员来担当MC吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.51,0:00:43.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么开始进行第一回MC大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.34,0:00:51.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？ 从我开始吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.73,0:01:02.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎大家…来到放学后茶会的…演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.63,0:01:07.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写成演唱会  其实读作平安夜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.77,0:01:08.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真意是？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.71,0:01:11.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪边都很热闹…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.94,0:01:17.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷场了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.94,0:01:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NETA还不太行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.07,0:01:31.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MC大奖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.07,0:01:36.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其二  于是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.92,0:01:42.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家来到放学后茶会的演唱会…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.27,0:01:50.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还早了一百年呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.00,0:01:57.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实很意外呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.96,0:02:00.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把人赶跑了不就没意义了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.10,0:02:11.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MC大奖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.10,0:02:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其三  全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.99,0:02:24.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.62,0:02:30.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻·音·部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.32,0:02:38.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…真的很难评价啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.15,0:02:48.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MC大奖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.15,0:02:53.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其四  英雄来迟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.89,0:02:57.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.71,0:02:59.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是放学后茶会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.80,0:03:03.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为MC啊  你们看  麦克风测试的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.25,0:03:07.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有去咔咔地敲麦克风吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.05,0:03:10.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直以为是这个省略呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.59,0:03:13.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麦克（Mic）咔咔（Concon）就叫MC
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.30,0:03:16.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有人说这是错的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.26,0:03:20.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「漫谈  Comical」才叫MC
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.99,0:03:22.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有人说那也是错的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.96,0:03:27.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司仪（Master of Ceremonies）的略称才叫MC啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.64,0:03:28.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厉害吧  
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.80,0:03:30.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Master哦  Ceremonies的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.28,0:03:32.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.85,0:03:35.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种安定感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.43,0:03:37.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当之无愧的Master of Ceremonies
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.06,0:03:40.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MC大奖获主出现了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.13,0:03:44.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这比赛根本没什么意义啊…


